I forget who was asking,  but I didn't miss the show.  I am just used to having time set aside mon-wed for the shows,  and with it being wed-fri this week I was already busy.   Didn't know he was doing wed-fri until the beginning of this week.

Should be on track next week though.  Peace & Love.
